erform-massive-new-song-billboards-nme-radar-3796475">英语老师去年在巡回赛上演奏了一条名为“广告牌”的新曲目</a>。</p><p>今年还将看到<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fontaines-d-c-announce-massive-2025-manchester-show-at-wythenshawe-park-3797642">英语老师在曼彻斯特的Fontaines DC开放</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bearded-theory-adds-paul-heaton-english-teacher-nadine-shah-the-lottery-winners-and-more-to-stacked-2025-line-up-3828411">在德比郡的胡须理论上演出</a>，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/wide-awake-2025-marie-davidson-nadine-shah-warmduscher-gurriers-new-names-3816851#:~:text=The%202025%20instalment%20promises%20seven,still%20to%20be%20announced%E2%81%A0.">出现在伦敦的Wide Awake Festival上</a>。</p><p>邮政的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/english-teacher-announce-biggest-ever-uk-headline-tour-for-winter-2025-buy-tickets-3841103">英语老师宣布，2025年冬季的英国最大的标题巡回赛</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
